      • setMmConnection

        protected void setMmConnection(Connection mmConnection)
        Sets safely a database connection to the mega-map, used to clean PDB xrefs from theoretical models coming from UniProt WS.
        Parameters:
        mmConnection - a database connection (can be null, in which case no attempt will be made to use it).

      • fixPdbXrefs

        protected uk.ac.ebi.ep.enzyme.model.EnzymeModel fixPdbXrefs(uk.ac.ebi.ep.enzyme.model.EnzymeModel summary)
        Fixes any cross references to PDB by querying the mega-map, which only contains PDB entries from empirical methods, no theoretical models.
        Note that this method will do nothing if no MegaMapper is set for this UniprotCallable.
        Parameters:
        summary - a summary to fix.
        Returns:
        the same summary, fixed.
